column5: I figure "self-help" is a good thing. Spiritual "stuff" like meditation,AA,prayer,relaxation techniques, etc..add to our well-being & daily life.
Danbo.. I went to a Seminar last night called The Laws of Attraction. Check out the book by Micheal Losier... excellent stuff if you are into it
Will check the links out later.  The wife has the book and video and there is a lot of positive stuff there.
How to grieve losses is important too..  http://www.helpguide.org/mental/grief_loss.htm

Last week my wife rented that movie, and she is trying it out.  She was 15 pts behind in my hockey pool last week, now she is within 5. She kept saying "i am going to win the pool, I am going to win the pool"....  I hope the attraction is enough for her to gain the 5 points needed! (Then she will LOVE hockey pools, and not mind if I continue to run them)
